data.title: The Journal News
data.meta_description: Blake Lively and Bruce Willis have joined the cast of Allen's yet-to-be-titled film.
data.text:
Woody Allen's next film will star two of Bedford's best.

Blake Lively and Bruce Willis have joined the cast of Allen's yet-to-be-titled film. Their costars will include Jesse Eisenberg, Kristen Stewart, Jeannie Berlin, Parker Posey and Corey Stoll. The movie will begin shooting in New York and Los Angeles later this month.

Lively and Willis have both been away from home their Bedford homes while working on other projects in recent weeks. Lively was recently photographed shooting the drama 'All I See is You' in Barcelona. Willis is in Los Angeles working on an untitled film.

Will the famous locals share much screen time in Allen's latest? We'll have to wait to find out. The movie's plot has not been revealed.

Photo: Getty
